  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>I stumbled over the problem that using the destroyAll() method requires overriding the destroyMapViews() method in the MapViewerTemplate, as otherwise a double destroy of the FramebufferController will cause a crash. </p>

<p>I think this is somewhat undesirable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

